    {
      "chinese": "男人學習蓋屋、打獵、耕田、烘烤芋頭乾、磨刀、裝卸、取材；女人學習廚藝、縫衣、刺繡、編織、做小米糕餅、釀小米酒、餵豬、藏物、打掃、整理環境、照顧孩子，去田裡似乎比男人還要多，做女人真不容易。以上的技能精巧熟練，便會被稱讚、心儀、信任、羨慕，許多人來追求、相親、戀愛和聯姻。",
      "ab": "Ku sawvalay kiacaucakuane ki tuadaane, waalupu, tuaumauma, thingale kutu, tuadreme, suragele, thurade. Kay labaibay kiacakuane ki marasiakay ki aga, caisi ki laimay, pacase ki laimay, tinunu, tuabay, tukabavane, pudeethe ki beeke, sekete ku taleke, lripethele, tulrilringulu, ngudalrane, miaki makakalra ki akibulruane ki sawvalay, sirapale ki lalake, makucingalre aababay, ai, lukalrigilinga, kiadrengedrengere, kiamurikay, kiasudralru, kiapusamalra, ngualay kuini si kimurikay ku lalake ku sawvalay si labaibay kela kiliase, mupapalange, mathaetharevenga.",
